msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.186:0.2"
msgid "17. Saṭṭhipeyyālavagga"
msgstr "17. Sixty Abbreviated Texts"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 186. Ajjhattātītāniccasutta → atītāniccasuttaṃ (bj) | atītena (nava) 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.186:0.3"
msgid "186. Ajjhattātītāniccasutta"
msgstr "186. The Interior Was Impermanent in the Past"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.186:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Cakkhu, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ atītaṃ … pe … jivhā aniccā atītā … pe … mano "
"anicco atīto."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, in the past the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind were "
"impermanent."

msgctxt "sn35.186:1.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako cakkhusmimpi nibbindati … pe … "
"jivhāyapi nibbindati … pe … manasmimpi nibbindati."
msgstr ""
"Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with the eye, ear, "
"nose, tongue, body, and mind."

msgctxt "sn35.186:1.3"
msgid ""
"Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re "
"freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed."

msgctxt "sn35.186:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti "
"pajānātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been "
"completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any "
"state of existence.’”"
